defaultcells killed off the cells that
default had not got the desired gene (the antibiotic sulfonylurea was used by BASF in analogous way
default). So began the dominance of Monsanto with their 
defaultglyphosate
default 
defaulttolerant
default soya, maize
default, oilseed rape, sugar beet
default and cotton. Patents 
defaultare now expiring on some of the varieties
default 
defaultso
