defaultBayer developed varieties of oilseed rape, rice, soya and sugar beet tolerant to the herbicide 
defaultglufosinate
default. 
defaultG
defaultene transfer is attractive to plant breeders as it allows identified beneficial genes to be added to existing good varieties relatively easily. This is to be contrasted
default 
