default GM technology is a precise way of introducing a gene for a specific effect which causes minimal changes to the original DNA.
default 
defaultIt is theoretically possible that the introduction 
defaultof one or two genes 
defaultmight alter the performance of existing genes that might turn out to be deleterious.
default This aspect is addressed in the safety evaluation of GM crops.
